<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../042/645042.xml">
New York City</link></village>
.</p>
<p>

Vance is a big supporter of <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../945/324945.xml">
Boys &amp; Girls Clubs of America</link>. He is an alumnus of the Detroit Boys &amp; Girls Club, and was recently inducted into the Alumni Hall of Fame for all of Boys &amp; Girls Clubs of America.</p>

